data.description: **Seller concessions / credits to be given to the buyer(s) towards closing costs, rate reduction, down payment, etc...with an agreeable offer/contract! Welcome to this well maintained one-story condominium, offering effortless living on the first floor. Nestled within the sought-after community of Summer's Bend on the Ashley, this residence enjoys a prime location along the Ashley River.The property boasts convenient access to an inclusive pool, a cozy fireplace, an outdoor kitchen, and a private community dock. Here, residents can relish in the serene ambiance, observing wildlife and capturing picturesque river and marsh views, complete with breathtaking sunsets and sunrises.The interior of the home features three bedrooms and two full bathrooms, all situated on the first floor. The well-designed floor plan positions two bedrooms with their own bath on one wing, while the Master Suite occupies the opposite wing. The expansive Master Bedroom Suite is bathed in natural light, courtesy of numerous windows, and showcases a generously sized walk-in closet with shelving. The master bathroom is both stylish and functional, boasting two separate his and her vanity sinks, a garden tub, and a standalone walk-in shower, all adorned with tile flooring and walls.  Pocket doors are provided at the entrance to the Master Bathroom and into the commode, shower and tub area.  To note, all entry doors leading into each room adhere to ADA compliance standards, ensuring accessibility for wheelchairs.  The kitchen is a focal point, featuring a spacious counter for culinary endeavors and seamlessly connecting to the large living room. Equipped with stainless steel appliances, including those that convey with the property, and a convenient pantry, the kitchen is a chef's delight. Adjacent to the kitchen, a separate and spacious dining room provides an ideal setting for hosting gatherings.  The living room is enhanced by a gas fireplace and an abundance of windows, allowing for a bright and inviting atmosphere. Interior shutters adorn every window, adding a touch of sophistication throughout. All bedrooms and the living room are equipped with ceiling fans for added comfort, and the separate laundry room includes a washer and dryer that convey with the property.  Exterior features include a detached extended one-car garage with shelving, offering ample space for both parking and storage. The rear of the property boasts a sizable outdoor area with a covered patio and a screened-in porch, providing a perfect retreat to savor coffee, evening cocktails, and the daily visits of beautiful birds to the community.   Notably situated within the distinguished Dorchester II school district, this property is conveniently located in proximity to shopping, restaurants, and features walking paths within the community. The tranquility of this quiet neighborhood provides a serene retreat away from the bustling activities of daily life. This residence is truly a pleasure to call home.
